{"tid":936931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再俾人spin, 以報失黎用舊護照黎入境加拿大係冇撚可能","createTime":"2018-12-11T07:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T23:56:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":141,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd864c9c64286992bb327871bb079ee8edae1c9","tid":936931,"uid":48083,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:10:27.000Z","msg":"1. <a href=\"https://www.interpol.int/INTERPOL-expertise/Border-management/SLTD-Database\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interpol.int%2FINTERPOL-expertise%2FBorder-management%2FSLTD-Database&d=%2FsacCtyq6%2Fd%2BFgkrOoXRNi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5de37789\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.interpol.int/INTERPOL-expertise/Border-management/SLTD-Database</a><br />\n<br />\n報失左既護照要報上包括intelpol之類既國際database架，加拿大點會唔知本護照係咪invaild左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果無報上去令加拿大照當佢vaild港府一樣係有錯無跟足報失程序要上身。<br />\n<br />\n一個post有人講完有國際database，就即刻潛，然後第個post又黎個係咁洗太平地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.依家政府已經番查過, 有人報失呃政府一定知<br />\n777同入境處話佢改名咋, 冇話佢報失<br />\n哩個可能性已經排除咗<br />\n除非777用整個政府信用去為佢講一個好易督爆既大話"},{"pid":"aee4370176a0c19c30803ebd794d1b06b1146dce","tid":936931,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a445c1bd8f0a1be25f60009462acbd26e5cdc0d","tid":936931,"uid":25952,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:17:22.000Z","msg":"代表lihkg 好多5毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd96c4e9902f321272ffeb4f01f03a0133002775","tid":936931,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfdfb6f30e7015b878802f516f2768398b318d7d","tid":936931,"uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"第一點credit to 櫻花巴打"},{"pid":"a98a06fc2adc1c7765c778592578423004d5a59d","tid":936931,"uid":20723,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"cfdfb6f30e7015b878802f516f2768398b318d7d","tid":936931,"uid":48083,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:21:32.000Z","msg":"第一點credit to 櫻花巴打"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:23:52.000Z","msg":"仲要比多個CREDIT 比陳生教識左我地PASSPORT防偽 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46645c8b0a67a76d6071b72b750e97f6eb2cf13","tid":936931,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:29:41.000Z","msg":"呢個咪即係有個國際刑警主席回國後被補然後辭職嘅國際刑警？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.interpol.int/INTERPOL-expertise/Border-management/SLTD-Database\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.interpol.int%2FINTERPOL-expertise%2FBorder-management%2FSLTD-Database&d=%2FsacCtyq6%2Fd%2BFgkrOoXRNi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=5de37789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.interpol.int/INTERPOL-expertise/Border-management/SLTD-Database</a><br />\n<br />\nStolen and Lost Travel Documents database<br />\nINTERPOL&rsquo;s database of Stolen and Lost Travel Documents (SLTD) enables INTERPOL National Central Bureaus (NCBs) and other authorized law enforcement entities &ndash; such as immigration and border control officers &ndash; to ascertain the validity of a travel document (passports, identity documents, visas) in seconds.<br />\n<br />\nThe SLTD database was created in 2002, following the 11 September 2001 terrorist attacks in the USA, in order to help member countries secure their borders and protect their citizens from terrorists and other dangerous criminals using fraudulent travel documents. <br />\n<br />\nHow it works<br />\nDetails of stolen and lost passports are submitted directly to the STLD database by INTERPOL NCBs and law enforcement agencies via INTERPOL&rsquo;s ﻿I-24/7 secure global police communication system. Only the country which issued a document can add it to the database.<br />\n<br />\nLaw enforcement officials at INTERPOL NCBs and other locations with access to INTERPOL&rsquo;s databases through the I-24/7 system &ndash; such as airports and border crossings &ndash; can query the passports of individuals travelling internationally against the SLTD, and immediately determine if the document has been reported as lost or stolen so they can take the necessary actions."},{"pid":"0045915f00ba1b2ca247b549ce178e709f8fa92a","tid":936931,"uid":45353,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:39:36.000Z","msg":"國際database唔知<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但intenert年造到資料第一時間互通幾難<br />\n<br />\n結果搵私穩拋我<br />\n你要入人地地方就同意左基本個人資料<br />\n做免簽真係對香港講過&quot;信&quot;字咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n難為我仲認真搵比陌生人入屋做例子<br />\n結果根本死詭理得咩例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e278b05d8538e228ae17ea73e534be5fdacdff5","tid":936931,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T07:57:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe29bb30874d4a6b15541185749c8d535c60fad0","tid":936931,"uid":146769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:00:11.000Z","msg":"推上報"},{"pid":"4908207143c82f1f7536e6849ed9f9481a6df044","tid":936931,"uid":77143,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T08:03:10.000Z","msg":"CC台嘅人永遠先入為主<br />\n你呢個post好快沉底<br />\n佢地唔會願意去相信同自己立場唔同